<div class="about-2 about part wrapper">
  <div class="about-text">
    <h3 class="swirl pink">Profile</h3>
    <h6>When I'm not fiddling around with technical stuff I love to cook, polish my boots, instagramming the latest fades of my jeans and enjoying other well designed goods. I deeply care about design and especially products that have a sustainable relationship with the world around us that instead of feeling worn out and out of date gains patina and become a natural part of people's life.</h6>
